column16: Chris Heston intentionally walks David Peralta.
Jake Lamb doubles (5) on a line drive to center fielder Denard Span.   Jean Segura scores.
Jean Segura singles on a soft ground ball to shortstop Brandon Crawford, deflected by second baseman Joe Panik.   Phil Gosselin scores.
Brandon Drury pops out to first baseman Brandon Belt in foul territory.
Chris Owings out on a sacrifice bunt, first baseman Brandon Belt to second baseman Joe Panik.   Phil Gosselin to 2nd.
Phil Gosselin singles on a line drive to center fielder Denard Span.
Nolan Arenado lines out to third baseman Matt Duffy.
Carlos Gonzalez grounds out, second baseman Kelby Tomlinson to first baseman Brandon Belt.   DJ LeMahieu to 3rd.    Trevor Story to 2nd.
Trevor Story walks.   DJ LeMahieu to 2nd.
Jorge De La Rosa grounds out, shortstop Brandon Crawford to first baseman Brandon Belt.
Ben Paulsen singles on a ground ball to left fielder Angel Pagan.   Mark Reynolds scores.  Ben Paulsen advances to 2nd, on a throwing error by left fielder Angel Pagan.
Mark Reynolds doubles (3) on a fly ball to center fielder Denard Span.   Carlos Gonzalez scores.    Nolan Arenado scores.    Gerardo Parra scores.
Chris Heston intentionally walks Gerardo Parra.
Nolan Arenado doubles (3) on a sharp fly ball to left fielder Angel Pagan.   Jorge De La Rosa scores.    DJ LeMahieu scores.    Carlos Gonzalez to 3rd.
Nolan Arenado singles on a ground ball to left fielder Angel Pagan.   Carlos Gonzalez to 2nd.

Charlie Blackmon grounds out to first baseman Brandon Belt.
Chris Rusin pops out to shortstop Brandon Crawford.
With Chris Rusin batting, DJ LeMahieu caught stealing 2nd base, catcher Trevor Brown to shortstop Brandon Crawford.
